{"image_id": "PHM_2009_page_49", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "Liquidity and Capital Resources (continued)", "bbox": [118.8, 65.4, 515.0, 86.2]}, {"text": "Seasonality", "bbox": [118.8, 115.3, 214.9, 136.2]}, {"text": "We experience variability in our quarterly results from operations due to the seasonal nature of the homebuilding", "bbox": [160.5, 152.8, 1119.0, 173.7]}, {"text": "industry. Historically, we have experienced significant increases in revenues and cash flow from operations during the", "bbox": [118.8, 177.8, 1119.2, 198.7]}, {"text": "fourth quarter based on the timing of home settlements. However, the challenging market conditions experienced since", "bbox": [118.8, 202.8, 1119.1, 223.7]}, {"text": "early 2006 have lessened the seasonal variations of our results. Given the current significant uncertainty in the", "bbox": [118.8, 227.8, 1119.1, 248.7]}, {"text": "homebuilding industry, we can make no assurances as to when and whether our historical seasonality will recur.", "bbox": [118.8, 252.9, 1055.6, 273.7]}, {"text": "Contractual Obligations and Commercial Commitments", "bbox": [118.8, 315.5, 620.5, 336.3]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes our payments under contractual obligations as of December 31, 2009:", "bbox": [160.5, 352.9, 1017.5, 373.7]}, {"text": "Payments Due by Period", "bbox": [707.3, 398.8, 926.7, 419.7]}, {"text": "($000’s omitted)", "bbox": [744.8, 419.7, 889.0, 440.5]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [543.1, 448.8, 590.6, 469.7]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [671.1, 448.8, 712.8, 469.7]}, {"text": "2011-2012", "bbox": [771.8, 448.8, 862.1, 469.7]}, {"text": "2013-2014", "bbox": [896.8, 448.8, 987.1, 469.7]}, {"text": "After 2014", "bbox": [1019.9, 448.8, 1114.3, 469.7]}, {"text": "Contractual obligations:", "bbox": [118.8, 482.1, 319.9, 502.9]}, {"text": "Long-term debt (a) . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [139.6, 507.1, 493.9, 527.9]}, {"text": "$7,229,839", "bbox": [520.0, 507.1, 613.8, 527.9]}, {"text": "$314,937", "bbox": [652.9, 507.1, 731.0, 527.9]}, {"text": "$ 973,000", "bbox": [770.1, 507.1, 863.9, 527.9]}, {"text": "$1,715,823", "bbox": [895.2, 507.1, 988.9, 527.9]}, {"text": "$4,226,079", "bbox": [1020.2, 507.1, 1114.0, 527.9]}, {"text": "Operating lease obligations . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [139.6, 532.1, 493.9, 552.9]}, {"text": "256,092", "bbox": [546.1, 532.1, 613.8, 552.9]}, {"text": "54,162", "bbox": [673.7, 532.1, 731.0, 552.9]}, {"text": "76,536", "bbox": [806.6, 532.1, 863.9, 552.9]}, {"text": "48,992", "bbox": [931.6, 532.1, 988.9, 552.9]}, {"text": "76,402", "bbox": [1056.7, 532.1, 1114.0, 552.9]}, {"text": "Other long-term liabilities (b) . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [139.6, 557.1, 493.9, 578.0]}, {"text": "2,337", "bbox": [566.9, 557.1, 613.8, 578.0]}, {"text": "990", "bbox": [699.8, 557.1, 731.0, 578.0]}, {"text": "1,068", "bbox": [817.0, 557.1, 863.9, 578.0]}, {"text": "129", "bbox": [957.7, 557.1, 988.9, 578.0]}, {"text": "150", "bbox": [1082.7, 557.1, 1114.0, 578.0]}, {"text": "Total contractual obligations (c)", "bbox": [139.6, 590.5, 408.2, 611.3]}, {"text": ". . . . . . .", "bbox": [426.2, 590.5, 493.9, 611.3]}, {"text": "$7,488,268", "bbox": [520.0, 590.5, 613.8, 611.3]}, {"text": "$370,089", "bbox": [652.9, 590.5, 731.0, 611.3]}, {"text": "$1,050,604", "bbox": [770.1, 590.5, 863.9, 611.3]}, {"text": "$1,764,944", "bbox": [895.2, 590.5, 988.9, 611.3]}, {"text": "$4,302,631", "bbox": [1020.2, 590.5, 1114.0, 611.3]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [118.8, 652.5, 140.7, 671.2]}, {"text": "Represents our senior notes and related interest payments.", "bbox": [156.3, 652.5, 597.1, 671.2]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [118.8, 700.4, 140.7, 719.2]}, {"text": "Represents our limited recourse collateralized financing arrangements and related interest payments.", "bbox": [156.3, 700.4, 920.7, 719.2]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [118.8, 748.4, 139.6, 767.1]}, {"text": "We do not have any payments due in connection with capital lease or purchase obligations.", "bbox": [156.3, 748.4, 843.6, 767.1]}, {"text": "We are subject to the usual obligations associated with entering into contracts (including land option contracts) for", "bbox": [160.5, 796.8, 1119.1, 817.6]}, {"text": "the purchase, development, and sale of real estate in the routine conduct of our business. Option contracts for the", "bbox": [118.8, 821.8, 1119.1, 842.6]}, {"text": "purchase of land enable us to defer acquiring portions of properties owned by third parties and unconsolidated entities", "bbox": [118.8, 846.8, 1119.0, 867.6]}, {"text": "until we are ready to build homes on them. This reduces our financial risks associated with long-term land holdings. At", "bbox": [118.8, 871.8, 1119.2, 892.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009, we had agreements to acquire 16,421 homesites through option contracts. At December 31, 2009,", "bbox": [118.8, 896.8, 1119.2, 917.6]}, {"text": "we had $140.8 million of non-refundable option deposits and pre-acquisition costs related to these agreements.", "bbox": [118.8, 921.8, 1044.2, 942.7]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2009, we had $326.1 million of gross unrecognized tax benefits and $80.6 million of related", "bbox": [160.5, 971.8, 1119.0, 992.7]}, {"text": "accrued interest and penalties. We are currently under examination by various taxing jurisdictions and anticipate", "bbox": [118.8, 996.8, 1119.0, 1017.7]}, {"text": "finalizing the examinations with certain jurisdictions within the next twelve months. However, the final outcome of", "bbox": [118.8, 1021.8, 1119.2, 1042.7]}, {"text": "these examinations is not yet determinable. The statute of limitations for our major tax jurisdictions remains open for", "bbox": [118.8, 1046.9, 1119.1, 1067.7]}, {"text": "examination for tax years 1998-2008.", "bbox": [118.8, 1071.9, 432.4, 1092.7]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes our other commercial commitments as of December 31, 2009:", "bbox": [160.5, 1121.9, 954.4, 1142.7]}, {"text": "Amount of Commitment Expiration by Period", "bbox": [611.0, 1167.8, 1022.9, 1188.7]}, {"text": "($000’s omitted)", "bbox": [744.8, 1188.7, 889.0, 1209.5]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [543.1, 1217.8, 590.6, 1238.7]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [671.1, 1217.8, 712.8, 1238.7]}, {"text": "2011-2012", "bbox": [771.8, 1217.8, 862.1, 1238.7]}, {"text": "2013-2014", "bbox": [896.8, 1217.8, 987.1, 1238.7]}, {"text": "After 2014", "bbox": [1019.9, 1217.8, 1114.3, 1238.7]}, {"text": "Other commercial commitments:", "bbox": [118.8, 1251.1, 394.7, 1271.9]}, {"text": "Guarantor credit facilities (a) . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [139.6, 1276.1, 493.9, 1296.9]}, {"text": "$ 950,000", "bbox": [520.0, 1276.1, 613.8, 1296.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [652.9, 1276.1, 663.3, 1296.9]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [724.0, 1276.1, 731.0, 1296.9]}, {"text": "$750,000", "bbox": [777.9, 1276.1, 856.1, 1296.9]}, {"text": "$200,000", "bbox": [903.0, 1276.1, 981.1, 1296.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1037.6, 1276.1, 1048.0, 1296.9]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1089.7, 1276.1, 1096.7, 1296.9]}, {"text": "Non-guarantor repurchase agreements . . .", "bbox": [139.6, 1301.1, 494.0, 1321.9]}, {"text": "175,000", "bbox": [546.1, 1301.1, 613.8, 1321.9]}, {"text": "175,000", "bbox": [663.3, 1301.1, 731.0, 1321.9]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [849.1, 1301.1, 856.0, 1321.9]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [974.1, 1301.1, 981.1, 1321.9]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1089.7, 1301.1, 1096.7, 1321.9]}, {"text": "Total commercial commitments (b) . . . . . . .", "bbox": [118.8, 1334.4, 493.9, 1355.3]}, {"text": "$1,125,000", "bbox": [520.0, 1334.4, 613.8, 1355.3]}, {"text": "$175,000", "bbox": [652.9, 1334.4, 731.0, 1355.3]}, {"text": "$750,000", "bbox": [777.9, 1334.4, 856.1, 1355.3]}, {"text": "$200,000", "bbox": [903.0, 1334.4, 981.1, 1355.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1037.6, 1334.4, 1048.0, 1355.3]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1089.7, 1334.4, 1096.7, 1355.3]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [118.8, 1396.5, 140.7, 1415.2]}, {"text": "Includes capacity to issue up to $950.0 million in letters of credit, of which $529.2 million were outstanding at December 31,", "bbox": [156.3, 1396.5, 1119.2, 1415.2]}, {"text": "2009.", "bbox": [156.3, 1419.4, 198.5, 1438.2]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [118.8, 1467.3, 140.7, 1486.1]}, {"text": "Excludes performance and surety bonds of approximately $2.9 billion, which typically do not have stated expiration dates.", "bbox": [156.3, 1467.3, 1077.0, 1486.1]}, {"text": "39", "bbox": [608.6, 1540.8, 629.4, 1561.6]}]}